in the lodge, a cosy and warm ski fleece for women is an absolute necessity for all seasons and occasions. Montec's top fleeces for women are sure to make you feel comfortable and warm no matter where you're headed. With a wide selection of fleece jackets to pick from, including casual designs in colours like green and red, you're sure to find the perfect fit, style, and thickness that's ideal for every season. Pick your favourite easily and quickly online at Montec's store.</p>\n<h2>Functionality</h2>\n<p>Fleeces are versatile, lightweight, warm, and breathable, and they have lots of great features for winter sports. Equipped with essential equipment features like adjustable cuffs and hem, they come in various styles including full-zip and half-zips. You can wear them skiing and in all winter activities, providing warmth and comfort on the mountains.</p>\n<p>Our ski fleeces are made from recycled polyester, so they're both light and breathable, making them a perfect mid layer when wearing underneath a snow jacket. Whether you're skiing at the resorts, in the backcountry or just relaxing by the fire after a hard day out there, the zips allow you to regulate your body temperature - and keep you warm even if the weather turns cold. And because they feature a chimney collar, your neck has extra protection against wind and cold.</p>\n<h3>Fleeces: models, sizes and colours</h3>\n<p>Whether you prefer half-zip construction or a fleece hooded midlayer with a chimney collar, Montec has you covered with plenty of different options to choose from. Choose a ski fleece that fits your style and type of activity; all our designs guarantee the perfect fit and a laid back cool appearance. Montec's ski clothes are highly functional and ideal for all of winter's adventures.</p>\n<p>Here at Montec, we offer a wide range of colours to match your style and other ski gear, such as black, green, and red. Our size range goes from XS to XL, ensuring you can choose your perfect fit. Browse the collection and order your favourite for this season on the mountain.</p>\n<h2>Find the newest collection at Montecwear.com</h2>\n<p>Get your hands on the latest snow technical mid layers including hoodies and fleeces for women at Montec. Choose your favourite colours and shop easily online! Get in touch with our customer service team if any questions come up or if you need help with choosing the perfect fleece.</p></div></div><div id=\"layout-colors\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 0px; right: 0px; overscroll-behavior: contain; visibility: hidden;\"></div><button class=\"intercom-button\" aria-label=\"Open chat\"><div><svg class=\"intercom-svg\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 28 32\"><path d=\"M28 32s-4.714-1.855-8.527-3.34H3.437C1.54 28.66 0 27.026 0 25.013V3.644C0 1.633 1.54 0 3.437 0h21.125c1.898 0 3.437 1.632 3.437 3.645v18.404H28V32zm-4.139-11.982a.88.88 0 00-1.292-.105c-.03.026-3.015 2.681-8.57 2.681-5.486 0-8.517-2.636-8.571-2.684a.88.88 0 00-1.29.107 1.01 1.01 0 00-.219.708.992.992 0 00.318.664c.142.128 3.537 3.15 9.762 3.15 6.226 0 9.621-3.022 9.763-3.15a.992.992 0 00.317-.664 1.01 1.01 0 00-.218-.707z\"></path></svg></div></button><svg width=\"0\" height=\"0\" style=\"display:none\"><symbol id=\"rs-expand\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M12 7v10M7 12h10\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></symbol><symbol id=\"rs-minus\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M7 12h10\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></symbol><symbol id=\"rs-chevron-right-small\" width=\"6\" height=\"10\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M1 1L5 5L1 9\" stroke=\"#000\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></symbol><symbol id=\"rs-chevron-right\" width=\"8\" height=\"14\" fill=\"none\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M.293.293a1 1 0 0 1 1.414 0l6 6a1 1 0 0 1 0 1.414l-6 6a1 1 0 0 1-1.414 0 1 1 0 0 1 0-1.414L5.586 7 .293 